## Development

```bash
# Clone and setup
git clone https://github.com/rafaelpontezup/stkai-sdk.git
cd stkai-sdk
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Run tests with coverage
pytest --cov=src --cov-report=term-missing

# Lint and type check
ruff check src tests
mypy src

# Build docs locally
pip install -e ".[docs]"
mkdocs serve
```

